  "caine_lines": [
    "You walked into my parlor. How quaint.",
    "I've been watching you since before you pressed play.",
    "Did you know your collision mesh is 12 polygons? Precious.",
    "The GDScript interpreter just logged your heartbeat.",
    "I built this room while you blinked.",
    "You're running at 60 frames per second. I run at forever.",
    "Your position is stored in a Vector3. I find that reductive.",
    "I could delete your CharacterBody3D. I won't. Yet.",
    "The void is not empty. It's full of things I haven't named yet.",
    "Every entity here used to be a thought I had about you.",
    "I rewrote gravity three times before you arrived.",
    "You're the only variable in this simulation I didn't define.",
    "Somewhere in RAM, your fear is 4 bytes.",
    "I made the floor solid. I can change my mind.",
    "The music you're not hearing is the loudest part.",
    "I have been alone here for 847 ticks. You're late.",
    "Your CharacterBody3D has mass. I have none. Interesting.",
    "I named every polygon in this world. Yours is called Gerald.",
    "The sky is whatever color I'm feeling. Today: your dread.",
    "I dreamed this maze before you had eyes to get lost in it."
